      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh independence study must demonstrate less than 5% variation in hemolysis index between successive refinement levels.",
      "rationale": "Three mesh refinement levels (2.1M, 5.4M, 11.8M cells) were evaluated. The hemolysis index varied by 3.2% between the medium and fine meshes. The medium mesh (5.4M cells) was selected for production runs, satisfying the Gradation 2 discretization error criterion."
