      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental data were collected at flow rates of 2.5 and 5.0 L/min and rotational speeds of 2000, 2500, and 3500 RPM. CFD boundary conditions were set to match these conditions within ±1% tolerance. Temperature, fluid viscosity, and inlet turbulence intensity were documented and replicated."
