      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all five operating points at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values agreed with experimental measurements within 12% across all five flow-speed combinations. The relative hemolysis index RH remained below 1.0 for all worst-case geometry variants, meeting the acceptance criterion."
